{"tid":1421354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"任性的連登　夭折的三罷","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:58:28.000Z","uid":264369,"like":4,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9707f55e4cf91565919971e3df4736b8e19e27","tid":1421354,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:50:30.000Z","msg":"話明各有各做，連登仔大規模不合作運動卻遲唔做早唔做，偏偏要揀晌同一日做．<br />\n本來可以向社會以至國際清晰顯示香港各界對政權表達的不滿，年青人的付出已得到保守的成年人行動上的支持．但是，事情卻被硬生生變成僅是新常態下的另一天混亂而已．<br />\n市民搞三罷要付出的代價從來就比學生年青人搞活動高很多．京官如今卻坐擁海量大家送上的材料恥笑三罷只是靠堵塞交通造成的笑話．<br />\n能有 take two 嗎？不會，不敢，不值．<br />\n任性地屌吧，你們還能怎樣．<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a584e368deeeaf122e0adad0fd15eeecb43b8b79","tid":1421354,"uid":55936,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:52:55.000Z","msg":"上星期已經講過，冇人理，長老由淺黃變番藍！"},{"pid":"bfc1785a9f53901f876197ee99103541a60ec9a2","tid":1421354,"uid":51790,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:53:28.000Z","msg":"發現兩條三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b0cee10bf689425beb0f1f75771fd78d8cca09","tid":1421354,"uid":269681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a584e368deeeaf122e0adad0fd15eeecb43b8b79","tid":1421354,"uid":55936,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:52:55.000Z","msg":"上星期已經講過，冇人理，長老由淺黃變番藍！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:53:57.000Z","msg":"見風轉舵既就算啦"},{"pid":"99bc797ac329f5130acc6857a0668fa9a9e34a26","tid":1421354,"uid":40628,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a584e368deeeaf122e0adad0fd15eeecb43b8b79","tid":1421354,"uid":55936,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:52:55.000Z","msg":"上星期已經講過，冇人理，長老由淺黃變番藍！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:54:01.000Z","msg":"黃係唔會變藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最多變返唔想理<br />\n<br />\n你點叫一個黃絲撐政府"},{"pid":"0baffdb30d052fb7d3f0ffccf3bd681d3f8818c8"